/**
 * Enables and configures the Z3 Satisfiability Modulo Theories (SMT) solver
 * backend for the refinement process.
 *
 * Activating this theory allows the solver engine to delegate numerical
 * and string constraints to the Z3 solver for high-performance reasoning.
 *
 * This solver is activated by default.
 */
#theory z3.
